com/b.gif?host=wordpress.tv&blog=5089392&post=13253&subd=wptv&ref=&feed=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" /><div><a href=\"http://wordpress.tv/2012/09/04/siobhan-mckeown-killer-docs-for-killer-devs/\"><img alt=\"Siobhan McKeown: Killer Docs for Killer Devs\" src=\"http://videos.videopress.com/hezwyKBF/5150-04_killer_docs_for_killer_devs_siobhan_mckeown_std.original.jpg\" width=\"160\" height=\"120\" /></a></div>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 05 Sep 2012 01:41:40 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Steve Bruner\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:38;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:2:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"Alex King: Hiring: Web Application UI/UX Designer\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"http://alexking.org/?p=14342\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:72:\"http://alexking.org/blog/2012/09/04/hiring-web-application-uiux-designer\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1789:\"<p>We&#8217;re still in the process of filling the <a href=\"http://alexking.org/blog/2012/08/09/hiring-devs-project-manager-denver\">three positions I posted about previously</a> (technical project manager, front-end web developer and full-stack web developer), but we&#8217;ve just added another position that I&#8217;m really excited about. We are looking for someone to join our team specifically as a UI/UX lead for web applications.</p>\n<p>We do a bunch of different stuff at <a href=\"http://crowdfavorite.com\">Crowd Favorite</a> and we care deeply about creating great products with great user experiences. Part of that user experience is the admin-side of the CMS, web app, etc. We are building ambitious WordPress sites for well known clients, and want to make sure their experience managing their site is as awesome as the experience that the users of their site have.</p>\n<p>We also create our own products &#8211; some WordPress related, some internal, some just as fun projects. We want to make the interfaces for those sing as well. I think this is a terrific opportunity to work with a top-notch team that knows how to execute and won&#8217;t compromise on vision or UX/UI experience.</p>\n<p>Think you&#8217;re right right person for the job? Can&#8217;t wait to <a href=\"http://crowdfavorite.com/jobs/\">hear from you</a>.</p>\n<p>I&#8217;m also very proud to be advertising this position on the excellent <a href=\"http://www.randsinrepose.com/onejob-jobs.html\">Rands in Repose website</a> as part of his <a href=\"http://www.randsinrepose.com/archives/2012/08/12/one_job.html\">One Job</a> sponsorship. I&#8217;ve known Michael for a long time, and I&#8217;m thrilled to be in a position to be able to support his excellent work and present this opportunity to his audience.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 04 Sep 2012 19:35:06 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s: